    <section class="content-section" id="text-based-ai">
        <h2>Text-Based Generative AI</h2>
        <p>Text-based generative AI uses advanced models to generate coherent and contextually relevant text-based responses. It's like having a virtual writing companion at your fingertips, capable of assisting you in composing emails, articles, or even finding the best restaurants in your area.</p>

        <div class="key-concept">
            <h3>Microsoft Copilot: A Text-Generation Example</h3>
            <p>Microsoft Copilot exemplifies text-based generative AI, allowing users to create various forms of written content quickly and efficiently. Whether you need help drafting an email, creating a report, or brainstorming ideas, Copilot can assist by generating text that matches your requirements.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="image-container">
            <svg width="400" height="200" viewBox="0 0 400 200">
                <!-- Laptop/Device -->
                <rect x="100" y="60" width="200" height="120" rx="10" fill="#f0f0f0" stroke="#333" stroke-width="2" />
                <rect x="110" y="70" width="180" height="90" fill="#fff" stroke="#ddd" />
                
                <!-- Text Content -->
                <line x1="130" y1="90" x2="230" y2="90" stroke="#4B6EFB" stroke-width="3" />
                <line x1="130" y1="110" x2="260" y2="110" stroke="#4B6EFB" stroke-width="3" />
                <line x1="130" y1="130" x2="200" y2="130" stroke="#4B6EFB" stroke-width="3" />
                
                <!-- Woman at laptop -->
