            </svg>
            <p class="caption">Text-based AI tools assist in drafting content from emails to social media posts and beyond.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>Real-World Example: Volunteer Outreach</h3>
            <p>Imagine you want to find ways to give back to your community. You love volunteering, especially helping others, but are overwhelmed by the amount of available information. With Microsoft Copilot, you could:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Ask for non-profit organizations that support people with vision disabilities in your city</li>
                <li>Have Copilot draft an introduction email to a non-profit about their volunteer process</li>
                <li>Generate a structured outline for volunteer opportunities that match your availability and skills</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section" id="visual-generation">
        <h2>Text-to-Image Generation</h2>
        <p>Text-to-image generative AI allows users to describe a scene through text and have AI bring it to life visually. This type of AI interprets text descriptions to create images, making it an invaluable tool for everyday imagination and design tasks.</p>

        <div class="image-container">
            <svg width="400" height="200" viewBox="0 0 400 200">
                <!-- Text to Image Concept -->
                <rect x="50" y="70" width="100" height="60" rx="5" fill="#f9f9f9" stroke="#4B6EFB" />
                <line x1="60" y1="90" x2="140" y2="90" stroke="#333" stroke-width="1" />
                <line x1="60" y1="100" x2="120" y2="100" stroke="#333" stroke-width="1" />
                <line x1="60" y1="110" x2="130" y2="110" stroke="#333" stroke-width="1" />
                
                <!-- Arrow -->
                <line x1="160" y1="100" x2="200" y2="100" stroke="#FB4B4B" stroke-width="2" />
                <polygon points="200,100 190,95 190,105" fill="#FB4B4B" />
                
                <!-- Image Result -->
                <rect x="210" y="50" width="140" height="100" rx="5" fill="#f9f9f9" stroke="#4B6EFB" />
                
                <!-- Bus in Image -->
                <rect x="230" y="90" width="90" height="40" rx="5" fill="#FB4B4B" />
                <rect x="240" y="100" width="20" height="15" fill="#fff" />
                <rect x="270" y="100" width="20" height="15" fill="#fff" />
                <circle cx="240" cy="135" r="8" fill="#333" />
                <circle cx="310" cy="135" r="8" fill="#333" />
                
                <!-- Bird on Bus -->
                <path d="M 290 80 Q 300 70, 310 80 T 330 80" fill="none" stroke="#6E4BFB" stroke-width="2" />
                <circle cx="310" cy="75" r="5" fill="#6E4BFB" />
            </svg>
            <p class="caption">Text-to-image AI transforms descriptive text into visual representations.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="key-concept">
            <h3>DALL·E Integration in Microsoft Designer</h3>
            <p>AI models like DALL·E are integrated into Microsoft Designer, which is a feature within Image Creator in Microsoft Copilot. By inputting a description, Microsoft Designer leverages DALL·E to turn conceptual ideas into virtual reality, allowing for creative visualization without advanced design skills.</p>
        </div>

        <p>For example, if you're creating a birthday invitation for your child's upcoming fifth birthday with a "rainbow giraffe" theme, you might struggle to find such specific decorations. Using Copilot's creative style, you could generate a custom image of a rainbow giraffe with the number 5, creating a unique design element for the invitation.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section" id="audio-video-ai">
        <h2>Audio and Video Generative AI</h2>
        <p>Generative AI isn't limited to text and images. Advanced models can now create audio content and even generate or enhance video content, opening new possibilities for multimedia creation.</p>

        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>Audio Generative AI</h3>
            <p>This form of AI can compose music or generate realistic sound effects. It can even replicate human voices for podcasts or virtual assistants, all from a set of parameters or a piece of text. Emerging applications enable users to record a sample of their own voice, which the system can accurately replicate to create extended audio segments or even entire songs.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="image-container">
            <svg width="400" height="180" viewBox="0 0 400 180">
                <!-- Audio Generation Illustration -->
                <rect x="50" y="40" width="300" height="100" rx="10" fill="#f9f9f9" stroke="#4B6EFB" stroke-width="1" />
                
                <!-- Sound Wave -->
                <path d="M 80 90 Q 100 60, 120 90 T 160 90 T 200 90 T 240 90 T 280 90 T 320 90" fill="none" stroke="#FB4B4B" stroke-width="2" />
                
                <!-- Microphone -->
