            </svg>
            <p class="caption">Audio generative AI creates or replicates sounds, music, and voices from input parameters.</p>
        </div>

        <h3>Video Generative AI</h3>
        <p>Video generative AI technology can create video content by learning from existing footage. It can animate characters, replicate environments, and even generate educational tutorials. This technology has practical applications like remastering old video footage to preserve and share memories with loved ones.</p>

